Aurelius Capital Management, LP: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 26, 2017 7:30 AM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Aurelius Capital Management, LP



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Aurelius Capital Management, LP is a privately owned investment manager. The firm invests in the public equity markets. Aurelius Capital Management, LP is based in New York, New York.


535 Madison Avenue22nd FloorNew York, NY 10022United States



Phone: 646-445-6500

www.aurelius-capital.com







Key Executives for Aurelius Capital Management, LP


Aurelius Capital Management, LP does not have any Key Executives recorded. 



Aurelius Capital Management, LP Key Developments

Co-Operative Bank Is Reportedly Close To Abandoning Its Search For A Buyer
Apr 30 17
Co-operative Bank plc is reportedly close to abandoning its search for a buyer and moving towards a second painful financial restructuring instead. The Co-operative Bank is expected to hire advisers from Houlihan Lokey to oversee a new rescue effort. It would allow existing backers, such as Aurelius Capital Management, LP and Silver Point Capital L.P., to plough more cash into the bank. City sources said KKR & Co. L.P. (NYSE:KKR), Oaktree Capital Management, L.P. and Apollo Global Management, LLC (NYSE:APO) were also considering buying equity.


